[This](https://github.com/libMesh/libmesh/blob/master/include/solution_transfer/radial_basis_functions.h) one also crashes in the same way, and is only 144 lines.  If I comment out all the explicit instantiations in the file, which are of the form:
```
template<>
inline
Real WendlandRBF<3,0>::operator()(Real rad) const
{
  if (rad > _rcut) return 0.;

  rad /= _rcut;

  return Utility::pow<2>(1.-rad);
}
```
then cppclean runs fine, for whatever that's worth.

