my whole point was to make it colorful by default for everyone, even if their layout was not specifically mentioned in LANG_COLOR. 
So here's my backward compatible suggestion. the `colors=(#xxx, #yyy)` remains as is, but we will first check for the `color` variable, after that for `LANG_COLOR` (as it was before), and if none of them was availble, we will check for the new `colors` variable.

